          <div class="app-code-snippet__container">
            <a class="app-link--copy" href="javascript:void(0);" aria-live="assertive">Copy<span class="ofh-u-visually-hidden"> custom Hero pattern</span> code</a>
            <pre><code class="language-js">{{- customHeroPatternCode | highlight('js') | safe -}}</code></pre>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h3>Accessibility</h3>
  <p>Keep the Hero heading semantic level correct for the page, which is typically <code>h1</code> for the primary page introduction.</p>
  <p>Check the focus order when both actions are present, and make sure the media alt text or decorative treatment matches the purpose of the image.</p>

